The chandelier and wood floors add to the home as soon as you walk in.The wood cabinets & island kitchen are inviting &perfect for entertaining. The downstairs master bedroom is large and has ample closet space w/tub and rain shower separate.The 2 bedrooms are combined w/ a Jack & Jill bath,and a extra bed and bath separate.Also  don"t miss the outdoor deck and yard!
